                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for synthesizing nicotinamide from 3-methylpyridine",
                    "一种由3-甲基吡啶合成烟酰胺的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a novel method for synthesizing nicotinamide from 3-methylpyridine, which comprises the following steps: taking benzylamine as a nitrogen source, synthesizing an amide compound under the catalysis of an oxidizing agent and ferric salt, and then reducing the amide compound into nicotinamide at room temperature by palladium on carbon and hydrogen. The synthesis method disclosed by the invention is mild in reaction condition, relatively low in equipment requirement, low in energy consumption, high in reaction selectivity, few in by-products and simple in post-treatment, and the purity of the product obtained by distillation can meet the industrial production requirement; meanwhile, the iron salt catalyst with lower cost and the Pd/C catalyst easy to recycle are used, so that the production cost is saved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种由3‑甲基吡啶合成烟酰胺的新方法，该方法以苄胺为氮源，在氧化剂和铁盐的催化下合成酰胺类化合物，然后通过钯碳和氢气在室温下将酰胺类化合物还原为烟酰胺。本发明的合成方法反应条件温和，对设备要求较低且耗能少，且反应选择性高，副产物少，后处理简单，经蒸馏得到的产物纯度即达到工业生产要求；同时，本发明使用成本较低的铁盐催化剂和易于回收再利用的Pd/C催化剂，有利于节约生产成本。"
                }
            ]
